  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Element
    Provides fluent access to RelativePositionFactory instances for: array elements List elements Iterable elements (requires IterableELResolver) Because this implementation uses unified EL facilities, growing lists/collections is not supported.
    Element.PositionFactory<PARENT,TYPE>
    Element RelativePositionFactory.
    Expression
    Fluent entry point for "expression at" RelativePositionFactory.
    Expression.PositionFactory<TYPE>
    Expression RelativePositionFactory.
    Keyed
    Provides fluent access to RelativePositionFactory instances for Map keyed values.
    Keyed.PositionFactory<K,V>
    Keyed value RelativePositionFactory.
    Keyed.Value<V>
    Fluent step.
    Property
    Fluent entry point for "property at" RelativePositionFactory.
    Property.PositionFactory<TYPE>  
    RelativePositionFactory<PARENT,TYPE>
    Describes an entity capable of producing RelativePositions.
    RelativePositionFactory.ReadWrite<PARENT,TYPE>
    Specialized subclass that advertises its products as RW.
